## Visualize the result {.smaller}


::: {.cell output-location='slide'}

```{.r .cell-code}
# save statistical test result
statres <- bfam |>
  anova_test(weight ~ sex)


ggboxplot(
  data = bfam,
  y = "weight",
  x = "family",
  fill = "family"
) +
  stat_anova_test()
```

